    "problemStatement": "Given two numbers,write a program to check whether a second input is a circular number of first input\n\nNote:Rotate the first number until you get the second number. If the second number found,then the second number is a circular number of first\n\n Example 1: 12345 45123 ->Circular\n\n 12345->51234->45123\n\n Example 2: 12345 45213 ->Not Circular\n\n 12345->51234->45123->34512->23451->12345",
